### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION & REGISTRATION
### ========================================

### 1. REGISTER a new ADMIN User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminpassword",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "nationalId": "1199080000000001"
}

###

### 2. REGISTER a new regular USER
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "USER",
  "nationalId": "1199080000000002"
}

###

### 3. LOGIN as ADMIN (To get Token)
# @name adminLogin
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminpassword"
}

###

### 4. LOGIN as regular USER (To get Token)
# @name userLogin
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ========================================
### SECURED CRUD TESTING FOR USERS (ADMIN ONLY)
### ========================================

### 1. READ all Users (GET) - Requires ADMIN Token
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. READ all Users (GET) - Will FAIL for regular USER
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### SECURED CRUD TESTING FOR DOCUMENTS
### ========================================

### 1. CREATE a new Document (POST) - Requires Token
POST http://localhost:8081/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "ID Card",
  "filePath": "/uploads/id-card.pdf",
  "applicationId": 1
}

###

### 2. READ all Documents (GET) - Requires Token
GET http://localhost:8081/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### SECURED CRUD TESTING FOR AUDIT LOGS (ADMIN ONLY)
### ========================================

### 1. READ all Audit Logs (GET) - Requires ADMIN Token
GET http://localhost:8081/api/auditlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}
Accept: application/json

